title: To The Last Drop of Blood (Do ostatniej kropli krwi) documentary
description:
A documentary about Polish underground metal scene. The movie follows guitarist Radek "Fred" Gizynski, who spent the best days of his youth playing metal in various bands and shared stages with future Polish heavy weights like Vader. He gave up music after the birth of his child, only to find out ten years and one divorce later, he has no purpose in life. Fred reforms the band with the help of other veteran musicians and some very young people. Just like in the 80's and 90's there's no money or fame in it, and this time he doesn't even have long hair.
